title: Trump Dog, Lebron James Tacos, Pimpin', Golden State and more.
itunes:title: Trump Dog, Lebron James Tacos, Pimpin', Golden State and more.
description:
Good morning and welcome to the ride! If you are into improving your situation, then this show is dedicated to you. The crew talk about Halloween, Our Houston crew members show love to The Nationals. Steph Curry breaks his hand. Trump gets caught in a lie surrounding a doctored photo. Pimpin' make his awaited return to discuss NFL week 9 and is excited about the two pimp capitals of the world. King James rents a taco truck to take care of first responders for the CA fires. Today in Closing Remarks, Big Dog talks about taking inventory and being grateful for what you have, plus so much more. Have a great weekend!!!
